name: Looking for Time #05
description:
Time is always moving. But our perception of time is directly related to our inner rhythm. In today's contemporary world, by immersing oneself in daily life, one can feel the speed of time by becoming aware. The "Looking for Time" collection shows the pace of time movement in various forms.
